==Related games==
The game is similar to a previous unpublished game by Jon Ritman, ''Soccerama''.<ref name=amstradmuseuminterview>{{Cite web |url=http://perso.wanadoo.es/amstradcpc/interviews/ritman.html |title=Interview with Ritman at amstradmuseum.com |access-date=2010-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607085726/http://perso.wanadoo.es/amstradcpc/interviews/ritman.html |archive-date=2009-06-07 |url-status=dead}}</ref> Later, in 1995, Jon Ritman tried to release ''Match Day III'', but the name of the game was changed to ''[[Super Match Soccer]]'' to avoid any potential legal issues.<ref name=amstradmuseuminterview />

